milestones.description: Marshall and Baptiste's 53-run partnership is WI's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 40 between Clive Lloyd and Joel Garner
Ijaz Faqih and Rashid Khan's 41-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 39 between Wasim Bari and Zaheer Abbas
Clive Lloyd has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (65) for WI, going past Viv Richards
